The '''1996–97 [[LEN Champions League]]''' was the ongoing 34th edition of [[LEN]]'s premier competition for men's [[Water Polo|water polo]] clubs. It ran from 1996 to 5 April 1997, and it was contested by 8 teams. The Final Four (semifinals, final, and third place game) took place on April 4 and April 5 in [[Naples]].

