[[File:Theater GT SuedTag.jpg|thumb|Theater Gütersloh]]
'''Theater Gütersloh ''' is a theatre for opera and drama performances in [[Gütersloh]], [[North Rhine-Westphalia]], [[Germany]]. The new building was designed by the architect [[Jörg Friedrich (architect)|Jörg Friedrich]]. It was opened in 2010.

